# UCAB - Client Setup (Installing React App)

## Objective

The objective of this task is to set up the React frontend application for the UCAB Cab Booking System using Vite. Vite provides a fast and modern development environment for React applications.

---

## Prerequisites

Before starting, ensure the following are installed:

- Node.js (v16 or above)
- npm (v8 or above)
- Visual Studio Code

---

## Step 1: Open Client Folder

Open the terminal in Visual Studio Code and navigate to the Client folder.

```bash
cd Client
